items.title: Los Sombreros in Scottsdale shows history does repeat itself
items.summary:
Los Sombreros co-owners Kurt Riske and Geoff Schuman know a thing or two about the restaurant industry with a combined 25 years’ experience, but in acquiring the South Scottsdale restaurant, it is their history with the establishment that really resonates. Both Riske and Schuman started their respective career paths working as servers and bartenders in the early 2000’s and are now honoring the tradition of Los Sombreros while updating it to meet the expectations of!
